description: AI and narration rules
globs:
  - backend/**
  - shared/**
alwaysApply: false
---

AI generation rules:
- LLM does not choose POI
- LLM does not choose trigger timing
- LLM does not decide story eligibility
- backend services provide a structured NarrativePlan
- guide style must come from guide profile JSON files
- output must respect target length, language, theme, and mode
- driving stories must be shorter and simpler than walking stories